    <item>
      <title>Projects</title>
      <link>https://alperenaksoy.de/en/projects/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://alperenaksoy.de/en/projects/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;-quranify--listen-to-the-quran-your-way&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  📖 Quranify – Listen to the Quran Your Way&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#-quranify--listen-to-the-quran-your-way&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quranify&lt;/strong&gt; is a beautifully minimalist app designed for listening to the Quran — completely free and ad-free. Enhance your spiritual experience with customizable nature sounds in the background.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-features&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  ✨ Features&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#-features&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🎧 &lt;strong&gt;Listen to the Quran&lt;/strong&gt;: Enjoy recitations from a variety of renowned Qaris.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🎙️ &lt;strong&gt;Multiple Reciters&lt;/strong&gt;: Choose from many beautiful and diverse voices.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🔊 &lt;strong&gt;Background Nature Sounds&lt;/strong&gt;: Add relaxing ambient sounds like:&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Rain 🌧️&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Birds 🐦&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Fire 🔥&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;And more&amp;hellip;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🎚️ &lt;strong&gt;Custom Volume Control&lt;/strong&gt;: Independently control the volume of the Quran and the nature sounds.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;📂 &lt;strong&gt;Playlist Support&lt;/strong&gt;: Add Surahs to your personal playlist.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;⭐ &lt;strong&gt;Favorites&lt;/strong&gt;: Mark your favorite Surahs for quick access.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🌙 &lt;strong&gt;Dark &amp;amp; Light Mode&lt;/strong&gt;: Switch between a clean light theme or a soothing dark mode.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🆓 &lt;strong&gt;Completely Free&lt;/strong&gt;: No ads, no subscriptions — just the Quran.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-screenshots&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  📱 Screenshots&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#-screenshots&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f0fc48b4-c82b-4d02-9e64-ae48130f72d8&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1040f60a-99db-4e08-8bbb-fb31c995711a&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/68530915-9c92-4aec-8e34-59a3af7037a4&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ba152ba0-51cd-4625-ae57-1d5f46b13965&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7849a324-85ba-491d-87e6-dce26e1718a9&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
